    <!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
      <meta charset="UTF-8" />
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
      <title>Full-Screen Hero Banner with Overlapping Image</title>
      <style>
        * {
          box-sizing: border-box;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
        }
    
        body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          background-color: #f9f9f9;
          line-height: 1.6;
        }
    
        .hero {
  position: relative;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e54c8, #8f94fb);
  color: white;
  height: 600px; /* fixed height instead of 90vh */
  padding: 100px 20px 80px;
  text-align: center;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
    
        .hero h1 {
          font-size: 48px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    
        .hero p {
          font-size: 20px;
          opacity: 0.9;
        }
    
        .overlap-image {
  max-width: 90%;
  margin: -60px auto 40px;
  display: block;
  z-index: 2;
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}
    
        .content {
          padding: 40px 20px;
          max-width: 800px;
          margin: 0 auto 60px;
          background-color: white;
          border-radius: 10px;
          box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
    
        .content h2 {
          font-size: 32px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          color: #333;
        }
    
        .content p {
          font-size: 18px;
          color: #555;
        }
      </style>
    </head>
    <body>
    
      <section class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Website</h1>
        <p>Delivering innovation one step at a time</p>
      </section>
    
      <img src="{{ 'modules/website/images/home/hero-banner-d.webp' | asset_url  }}" alt="" class="overlap-image">
    
      <section class="content">
        <h2>About Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We are a forward-thinking company dedicated to helping people and organizations harness the power of technology. 
          Our team of professionals is committed to delivering quality products and services that drive impact and growth.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're a startup or an enterprise, we tailor our solutions to meet your needs. Join us as we shape the future together.
        </p>
      </section>
    
    </body>
    </html>
    